nodes.text: A star system was located in a star cluster in the Unknown Regions. The system contained a small yellow sun. The Bargain Hunter came out of hyperspace a quarter light-year away from the system during the Skirmish between Progga and the Bargain Hunter. The captain of the Bargain Hunter, Dubrak Qennto, decided to enter the system and the Bargain Hunter came out near the yellow sun.
